#The very smart answer

engineer adopting the artist's hat :)

writer is trendy...


It is not that easy to pick up one single hat as all of them represent vital features for productive work and best results.
The brilliant performance of each of these roles requires flexibility, creativity, logic and communication. 

Writer shares his  experience with others polishing his own skills and knowledges. 
He use all his creativity to describe or even draw his code to make it legible and understandable for others. 
So not only Engineer adopts the artist's hat. Writer also some times has a chance to become an artist :)

